review:
- Extremely slow;
- When you leave the window, it resets everything you did;
- When ordering through the app, the deals NEVER work;
- Redeeming your rewards is like a lottery, no guarantees that it will work;
- The confirmation of anything takes a long time to be processed.

I would expect this of a brand new app from a small company, not Dairy Queen and not for this long.

